== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《瘋狂店員2》獲得了普遍好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據160篇專業影評，新鮮度63%，平均得分6.1／10<ref name="rottentom">{{rotten-tomatoes|id=clerks_2|title=Clerks II}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則獲得65分的正面評價<ref name="metacrit">{{metacritic film|id=clerks2|title=Clerks 2}}</ref>。主要被評論家稱讚電影中的幽默及獨特見解。

該片被[[IMDB|IMDB]]用戶評為2006年第三搞笑的電影<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/features/rto/2007/poll/bestresults |title=Clerks II poll at IMDB.com |access-date=2017-02-04 |archive-date=2017-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204171517/http://www.imdb.com/features/rto/2007/poll/bestresults |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及爛番茄的第9屆最佳喜劇<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/features/rtawards/movie_2006.php?r=9&mid=1159622&genre=200003 |title=Clercks II |author=Kevin Smith |date=2007-01-02 |work= |publisher=Rottentomatoes.com |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025131524/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/features/rtawards/movie_2006.php?r=9&mid=1159622&genre=200003 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

電影於2006年的[[第59屆坎城影展|第59屆坎城影展]]上放映後，獲得了觀影人們的八分鐘[[起立致敬|起立鼓掌]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://silentbobspeaks.com/?p=252 |title=Silentbobspeaks.com on the Cannes |access-date=2017-02-02 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109015607/http://silentbobspeaks.com/?p=252 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,197269,00.html#2 |title=Foxnews.com on Clerks II's reception at the Cannes |access-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522111344/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,197269,00.html#2 |archive-date=2013-05-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影在美國的首週末從兩千一百五十間戲院中獲得1006萬美元的票房<ref name="mojo" />。全球票房總計2700萬美元，對比500萬美元的預算來說可謂成功<ref name="mojo">[http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=clerks2.htm ''Clerks II''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=clerks2.htm |date=20170519163003 }} from [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]</ref>。

== 家庭媒體 ==
《瘋狂店員2》的[[DVD|DVD]]於2006年11月28日發行<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.newsaskew.com/includes/feature.shtml?id=EEVZApyZukyISxbZFT&style=single |title= Clerks II DVD Comments |date= 2006-09-10 |work= News Askew |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070927205900/http://www.newsaskew.com/includes/feature.shtml?id=EEVZApyZukyISxbZFT&style=single |archivedate= 2007-09-27 }}</ref>。根據《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》，電影在DVD的出租店與銷售獲得了約600萬美元的獲利，占總票房將近四分之一<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/home_entertainment/news/e3i4e2055a0ae81a852849d19f00f7e9894 |title='Superman' tops charts in single bound |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061210061452/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/home_entertainment/news/e3i4e2055a0ae81a852849d19f00f7e9894 |archivedate=2006-12-10 }}</ref>。

2007年1月16日，《瘋狂店員2》推出了[[HD_DVD|HD DVD]]，當中含有[[1080p|1080p]]高畫質的精選光碟和普通版DVD<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hddvd.highdefdigest.com/clerksii.html |title=HD DVD Review: Clerks II {{!}} High-Def Digest<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2017-02-04 |archive-date=2008-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080829104224/http://hddvd.highdefdigest.com/clerksii.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[高密度光碟格式之戰|高密度光碟格式之戰]]結束於2008年2月後，《瘋狂店員2》又於2009年2月3日發行了[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/1941/clerksii.html |title=Blu-Ray Review: Clerks II {{!}} High-Def Digest<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2017-02-04 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208095733/http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/1941/clerksii.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 續集 ==
2015年4月，史密斯透露，他將會拍攝《瘋狂店員3》及《[[耍酷一族|耍酷一族]]》的續集<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/kevin-smith-mallrats-2-2015/ |title=‘Mallrats 2′ Is Kevin Smith’s Next Film; He’ll Shoot ‘Clerks 3′ After |access-date=2017-02-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124615/https://www.slashfilm.com/kevin-smith-mallrats-2-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年2月9日，史密斯在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上透露，雖然劇本已經完成，但《瘋狂店員3》仍已作廢<ref>https://www.facebook.com/YesThatKevinSmith/posts/10154103461971930</ref>。

